# BF16 reference dumps (kldref) and Hessian sidecars (GPTQ) live external
# (~2.5 GB per kldref, ~34 GB for 9B Hessian). Use ../scripts/fetch-eval-refs.sh
# (lands in Step 4) to pull them locally. They're not in git — manifest.json
# is the index.
*.kldref.bin
*.hessian.bin
# Imatrix files (1-5 MB each) ARE committed — see qwen3.5-*-bf16.imatrix.gguf.
# They unblock `hipfire-quantize --awq` reproduction from a clean clone
# without an imatrix-collect prereq. Generated via
# crates/hipfire-runtime/examples/imatrix_collect.rs over wikitext-2-raw-v1
# with the model's BF16 tokenizer; deterministic given (corpus, model,
# tokenizer) so multiple developers regenerate to ~byte-similar files.
